### List products

GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/catalog/products?page=0&size=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}


### Filter by status and search

GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/catalog/products?status=ACTIVE&search=tee&featured=false HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}


### Fetch product details

GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/catalog/products/{{product_id}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}


### Create product

POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/catalog/products HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}

