### Update variant

PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/catalog/products/{{product_id}}/variants/{{variant_id}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}

{
  "active": true,
  "price": 27.50,
  "quantity": 12,
  "size": "M"
}


### Toggle variant status

PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/admin/catalog/products/{{product_id}}/variants/{{variant_id}}/status HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}

{
  "active": false
}


### Delete variant

DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/catalog/products/{{product_id}}/variants/{{variant_id}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}


